      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Add your <strong>cashew nuts </strong>to a small bowl, cover them with<strong> boiled water </strong>and set aside to soften</p>",
