      "instruction": "<p>Season your <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> on both sides with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat</p>",
