      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Once golden, reduce the heat to medium and add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and a couple of splashes of <strong>water</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for a further 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
