    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your<strong> bulgur wheat</strong>, <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock mix </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a pot with a lid with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and once boiling, reduce the heat to medium then cook, covered, for 7-9 min or until almost all the water has absorbed</p><p>Once done, remove the pot from the heat, fluff with a fork and set aside until later</p>",
